//! Integration Test Framework for {{ module_name|title }} Module
//!
//! This module provides the framework for running comprehensive integration tests
//! following the Backbone Framework testing patterns.
//!
//! Test Categories (5-Category Testing Pattern):
//! 1. Authentication Tests (401/403 validation)
//! 2. Success Tests (Happy path with DB/cache validation)
//! 3. Validation Tests (Missing fields, invalid values → 400)
//! 4. Business Logic Tests (Conflicts, not found, idempotency)
//! 5. Edge Cases (Boundaries, special characters)

